		<TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH=380>
			<BR>
			
			<H3>Apple Computer, Inc.<BR>
                                    Employment Information and Opportunities</H3>
			
Others can talk about boundaries. We don't believe they exist. Others can talk about risk-taking. We won't stand and wait. At Apple, we're already moving toward the next frontier. And there's no chance we'll turn back.
<P>
<B>So ask yourself one question.<BR>
<I>How far will I go to change the world?</I></B>
<P>
You know the technologies that will shape the next century have yet to be discovered. And you know that the best place to prove yourself is where no one will stand in your way. 
<P>
Right now, we're pushing forward with the most ambitious projects in our 20-year history. So if you've got the guts, the brains and the pure force of will to achieve what few others can--this is the time and place to do it. 
 <P>
If we sound like a company with lofty goals, no wonder. We have a history of achieving the impossible. And with your help, we'll do it again.  
<P><BR>
<B><A HREF="http://io.apple.com/cgi/eg/eg.acgi">Search Apple Jobs</A> using Apple e.g. search technology, or explore opportunities by discipline.</B>
<P>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="http://io.apple.com/cgi/imagemap/mapserve.acgi$employment/jobcats.map"><IMG SRC="./graphics/jobcats.gif" ALT="Opportunities at Apple" HEIGHT=140 WIDTH=370 BORDER=0 ISMAP USEMAP="#jobmap"></A>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE="-1">
<A HREF="./corpjobs.html">Corporate</A> | <A HREF="./hwengjobs.html">Hardware Engineering</A> |  <A HREF="./intljobs.html">International</A><BR>
<A HREF="./mktgjobs.html">Sales &amp; Marketing</A> |  <A HREF="./oprsjobs.html">Operations</A> | <A HREF="./servjobs.html">Service &amp; Support</A> | <A HREF="./swengjobs.html">Software Engineering</A>
</FONT>
</CENTER>
<P><BR>
<B>So, take a look at our current opportunities, and <A HREF="#howto">send us your resume</A>. Start changing the world!</B>

			<P><BR>

                                    <A HREF="benefits.html"><IMG SRC="./graphics/lilbene.gif" ALT="Benefits" HEIGHT=17 WIDTH=80 VSPACE="8" BORDER="0"></A><BR>
			Don't miss this chance to learn about Apple's excellent 
			<B><A HREF="benefits.html">Employment Benefits</A></B>.
			<P><BR>

                                    <A HREF="college.html"><IMG SRC="./graphics/lilcol.gif" ALT="College" HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=75 VSPACE="8" BORDER="0"></A><BR>
			Apple offers a variety of <B><A HREF="collegeint.html">College Hire and Internship positions,</A></B>
			including Student Work Experience in 
			our <B><A HREF="health.html">Health and Fitness Centers</A></B>.
			<P><BR>

			<A NAME="howto"><IMG SRC="./graphics/howto.gif" ALT="How to Apply" HEIGHT=20 WIDTH=127 VSPACE="8"></A><BR>
			If you are interested in career opportunities at
			Apple, please send your resume, indicating the position in which you 
     			are interested, to:
			
			 <P>
			<B>Apple Computer, Inc.</B><BR> 
			1 Infinite Loop, MS: 38-3CE <BR>
			Cupertino, CA  95014 <BR>
			Attn:  Professional Employment <BR>
			<P>
			<B>Fax:</B>  (408) 974-5691 <BR>
			
			<B>E-mail:</B> <A HREF="mailto:applejobs@apple.com">applejobs@apple.com</A> 
			(Please e-mail your resume by pasting it into the e-mail message body --
			<I>do not attach enclosures</I>.) <BR>
			<P>
			
			<B>Thank you for your interest in Apple Computer, Inc.</B>
			<P>
			
			Principals Only. No phone calls, please. 
			Apple Computer has a corporate commitment to the principle of diversity. 
			In that spirit, we welcome applications from all individuals.
			<P><BR>

